<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/705631-does-it-end-on-a-cliffhanger-so-you-have">Does it end on a cliffhanger so you have to read the next book straight after? Or can you read other books in between the first and second?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_705631'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F1722717.The_Declaration">like</a></span>

